  "title": "Wholesome Wilted Greek Bramley apples Hot-Pot-Vessel Stew",
  "description": "This satvik-friendly monsoon dish features bitter but flavorful bramley apples cooked in a hot-pot-vessel to perfection.",
  "cuisine": "greek",
